snippet.title: Rulent Tower VR - Trailer - Game Boy in VR - Play for Free!
snippet.description:
https://setsune.itch.io/rulent-tower-vr

Ever wanted to experience life in a Game Boy-era RPG? Now you can! Explore a small slice of Rulent Tower. Chat with your neighbors! Ring the receptionist's bell! Find secrets? Available in both PC VR and Oculus Quest standalone flavors, for FREE! If you don't have VR hardware, you can watch a walkthrough here: https://youtu.be/gS8ECaWkKt4

This is a 5 minute experience, so don't expect the moon. If you want to see more like it, please consider supporting my Patreon! https://www.patreon.com/setsune
